OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777442692
OL,3,CLocations where it typically takes
OL,4,Clonger to sell a home than last year
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe average length of time to sell a
OL,8,Fhome is just a day longer than a year
OL,9,Fago despite elevated mortgage rates,
OL,10,Falthough in London homes are taking
OL,11,Fnearly a week longer to be snapped up
OL,12,Ftypically, according to a property
OL,13,Fwebsite.
OL,15,FAcross the UK, the average time to
OL,16,Fsell a home is 33 days, just one day
OL,17,Flonger than last year, Zoopla said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
