SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777442692
OL,3,CLocations where it typically takes
OL,4,Clonger to sell a home than last year
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe London area stands out as being
OL,8,Fparticularly impacted by recent
OL,9,Fevents, with the average home there
OL,10,Ftaking six days longer to sell than a
OL,11,Fyear ago, the report found.
OL,13,FMortgage rates increased following the
OL,14,Fstart of the Middle East conflict, as
OL,15,Fswap rates, which are used by lenders
OL,16,Fto price mortgages, jumped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
