OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777442692
OL,3,CLocations where it typically takes
OL,4,Clonger to sell a home than last year
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FBut several major lenders have reduced
OL,8,Ftheir fixed mortgage rates in recent
OL,9,Fweeks amid falling swap rates, with
OL,10,Faverage fixed mortgage rates starting
OL,11,Fto plateau.
OL,13,FZoopla calculated average times to
OL,14,Fsell from properties being listed to
OL,15,Fbeing sold subject to contract.
OL,17,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,18,FZoopla, said: "Homes are taking just
OL,19,Fone day longer to sell than this time
OL,20,Flast year.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777442692
OL,3,CLocations where it typically takes
OL,4,Clonger to sell a home than last year
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,F"That is a strong result given
OL,8,Fincreased uncertainty and mortgage
OL,9,Frates rising sharply in March. Buyer
OL,10,Finquiries have rebounded after Easter
OL,11,Fand with mortgage rates starting to
OL,12,Ffall, we expect the market to remain
OL,13,Factive through the rest of the year.
OL,15,F"Households who need to move are
OL,16,Fgetting on with it though market
OL,17,Fconditions vary widely between North
OL,18,Fand South.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777442692
OL,3,CLocations where it typically takes
OL,4,Clonger to sell a home than last year
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,F"For sellers, the message is clear:
OL,8,Fwell-priced homes are still finding
OL,9,Fbuyers in the same time as last year
OL,10,Facross much of the country.
OL,12,F"For buyers, mortgage rates are
OL,13,Fdrifting lower and there is greater
OL,14,Fchoice of homes for sale. The best-
OL,15,Fvalue homes are moving quickly,
OL,16,Fparticularly in northern cities and
OL,17,FScotland, whereas the room for
OL,18,Fnegotiation is greater across southern
OL,19,Fregions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
