OL,4,Clonger to sell a home than last year
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FHere are average times to sell a home
OL,8,Fin days in the seven weeks to April 17
OL,9,F2025 followed by the seven weeks to
OL,10,FApril 17 2026, according to Zoopla (a
OL,11,Fbreakdown for Northern Ireland was not
OL,12,Fincluded):
OL,14,FScotland, 15, 15
OL,16,FNorth East, 28, 28
OL,18,FYorkshire and the Humber, 31, 31
OL,20,FNorth West, 28, 31
